trans-unit.target: Inneholder et sett med <xref href="System.Web.UI.ServiceReference"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: The ServiceReferenceCollection object contains a <xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference> object for each Web service that is registered in an AJAX-enabled ASP.NET page.
trans-unit.target: ServiceReferenceCollection objektet inneholder en <xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference>objekt for hver webtjenesteutvidelse som er registrert i en AJAX-aktiverte ASP.NET-side.</xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference>

trans-unit.source: Web services can be defined in the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control or in an associated <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> control.
trans-unit.target: Webtjenester kan defineres i den <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>kontrollen eller i en tilknyttet <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManagerProxy> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: You can add Web services to the ServiceReferenceCollection object declaratively by adding one or more `<asp:ServiceReference>` elements to a `<Services>` element inside the `<asp:ScriptManager>` element on the page, as shown in the following example.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til webtjenester til ServiceReferenceCollection objektet deklarativt ved å legge til én eller flere `<asp:ServiceReference>` elementer til en `<Services>` elementet i den `<asp:ScriptManager>` element på side, som vist i eksemplet nedenfor.

trans-unit.source: ``` <asp:ScriptManager ID="SM1" runat="server"> <Services> <asp:ServiceReference Path="Service1.asmx" /> <asp:ServiceReference Path="Service2.asmx" /> </Services> </asp:ScriptManager> ``` You can also programmatically add a <xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference> object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager.Services%2A> collection by using the <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601.Add%2A> method of the ServiceReferenceCollection class.
trans-unit.target: ``` <asp:ScriptManager ID="SM1" runat="server"> <Services> <asp:ServiceReference Path="Service1.asmx" /> <asp:ServiceReference Path="Service2.asmx" /> </Services> </asp:ScriptManager> ```Du kan også programmatisk legge til et <xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference>objekt i <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager.Services%2A>samlingen ved hjelp av <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601.Add%2A>metoden for ServiceReferenceCollection klasse.</xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.Collection%601.Add%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager.Services%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.ServiceReference>

trans-unit.source: Web services are registered with the <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager> control during the page's <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.PreRender> life cycle stage.
trans-unit.target: Webtjenester er registrert med den <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>kontrollen under sidens <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.PreRender>livssyklus fase.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.PreRender> </xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ServiceReferenceCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ServiceReferenceCollection"> </xref> klasse.
